--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    A vagrant setup that prepare a java8 environment inside an Ubuntu VM.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Quick start:
                $ vagrant up              # create and boot the vm
                $ vagrant ssh             # log into the vm
                $ vagrant ssh -- -A       # log into the vm with ssh forwarding
                $ vagrant suspend         # stop the vm

  More info on www.vagrantup.com and with $ vagrant --help

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
